metadata.name: SRF - Syria & Turkey Earthquake Relief
metadata.description:
Joining Jack Butchers effort to raise money for crisis relief in the wake of the 7.8 magnitude earthquake in Turkey and Syria.

Each NFT will be 0.0065 eth, the same amount as a $10 donation (as of 2/9/23). All proceeds will go to Doctors Without Borders via The Giving Block

Send ETH directly: 0xf3BFbC8701c2CF7c837CC30997f5da3829c5ABd8
